No information.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FF3B6A84FF4897BC1C28B91F" pageId="192" pageNumber="954" type="breeding">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFF3B6A84FF4897BC1C28B91F" blockId="192.[178,1386,287,833]" pageId="192" pageNumber="954">
<emphasis id="F6E0EAECFF3B6A84FF4897BC1F3BB934" bold="true" box="[180,315,485,518]" pageId="192" pageNumber="954">Breeding.</emphasis>
The single individual captured was an adult female that was lactating and had a single placentalscar.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
